The '''mid-mountain berrypecker''' or '''lemon-breasted berrypecker''' ('''''Melanocharis longicauda''''') is a species of [[bird]] in the family [[Melanocharitidae]]. It is found in the [[New Guinea Highlands]]. Its natural [[habitat]]s are [[subtropical or tropical moist lowland forest]] and subtropical or tropical moist [[montane forest]].

